AGI - The crime disputed to Maria Rosaria Boccia> has been requalified, listened today, for more than four hours from the pm of Rome. The entrepreneur of Pompei was initially accused of violence or threats to the political body and is now investigated for stalking.
The crime of injury remains, > to which the accusations of illicit interference in private life and diffamation are added. Context also false statements in the resume prepared for organizing events.
During the interrogation in front of the adjunct Giuseppe Cascini, the story of the head wound reported by the minister was also addressed. Boccia would deny the accusations by stating that the cut on the forehead would be due to a fall.
<div </div
In the course of the investigation, on at least one occasion, the tones rose. When the interrogation is finished, the chroniclers have asked Boccia for any 'tensions' with the magistrates. The entrepreneur did not respond and the defender denied.&nbsp; On September 21, the carabinieri searched the woman's house in Pompeii and seized, among other things, the smart glasses, used in the past by the woman to make a series of films even within the Chamber of Deputies.&nbsp;
"We responded" to the magistrates and "discussed the answers we gave. The interrogation lasted from 14 a hour," explained Boccia's lawyers, leaving Clodio square with his assistant.&nbsp;
